---
title: Beef & Black Bean Chili Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: This family-style chili bar will delight the whole crew! You’ll set out a spread of Southwest-spiced beef and black bean chili and steamy rice, plus toppings galore. Pile on cheddar cheese, scallions, diced red onion, and sour cream, then let everyone build their own perfect bowl. Order tortilla chips to make nachos or add crispy bacon for a smoky topper.

